{% extends 'email/base.text.twig' %}

{% block body %}
Hi {{ customer_name|default('there') }},

your support ticket has been successfully created. We have received your request and will get back to you as soon as possible.

TICKET DETAILS
--------------
Ticket No.:  #{{ ticket_id }}
Subject:     {{ ticket_subject }}
Category:    {{ ticket_category }}
Priority:    {{ ticket_priority }}
Created at:  {{ ticket_created_at }}

YOUR MESSAGE
------------
{{ ticket_message }}

View ticket: {{ ticket_url }}

You can check your ticket status at any time in your customer panel. Once our support team responds, you will receive another email notification.
{% endblock %}
